name: Apple
description: Red Delicious apples are a classic variety known for their distinctive bright red skin and sweet, crisp flesh. They are one of the most popular apple varieties worldwide and are favored for their appealing appearance and delightful flavor. These apples are typically medium to large in size and have a slightly elongated shape.

name: Bananas
description: Cavendish bananas are one of the most popular and widely consumed fruits globally. Known for their distinctive bright yellow color and sweet, creamy flesh, these bananas are a beloved tropical fruit. They are characterized by their slightly curved shape and convenient peel-and-eat packaging.

name: Pineapple
description: Pineapples are tropical fruits known for their sweet and tangy flavor, as well as their distinctive appearance. They are the fruit of the pineapple plant, which belongs to the Bromeliaceae family. Pineapples are prized for their delicious taste and versatility, making them a popular choice for both fresh consumption and culinary applications.

name: Grapes
description: Red seedless grapes are a delicious and widely enjoyed fruit known for their sweet and juicy flavor. They belong to the Vitis vinifera family and are a popular choice for snacking, adding to fruit salads, and incorporating into various culinary dishes. These grapes are distinguished by their vibrant red or purple skin and absence of seeds.

name: Berries
description: Mixed berries are a delightful assortment of small, colorful fruits, each bursting with a unique and vibrant flavor. They are nature's candy, cherished for their natural sweetness, juicy texture, and versatility. Mixed berries typically include a combination of strawberries, blueberries, raspberries, and blackberries, creating a medley of tastes and textures in every bite.

name: Citrus
description: Citrus fruits are a diverse and flavorful group of fruits known for their bright colors, refreshing taste, and tangy zing. These fruits belong to the citrus genus and are celebrated for their juicy flesh, vibrant aroma, and high vitamin C content. Citrus fruits include a wide range of varieties, each with its unique characteristics and culinary uses, but they all share a common zest for brightening up our palates.

name: Pears
description: Bartlett pears are a classic and beloved variety of pear, known for their sweet and succulent flesh, smooth texture, and distinctive pear shape. These pears are cherished for their juicy, refreshing flavor and versatile culinary uses. They are a member of the Pyrus genus and are available in various colors, with the most common being green when ripe.

name: Kiwi
description: Kiwi, a small yet powerful fruit bursting with vibrant color and a uniquely delicious taste. Our kiwis are carefully selected to ensure you experience the perfect blend of sweetness and tanginess with each bite

name: Melon
description: Melons, a delectable fruit that embodies the essence of freshness and sweetness. Handpicked at the peak of ripeness, our melons promise a mouthwatering experience with every bite.

name: Watermelon
description: Watermelon, scientifically known as Citrullus lanatus, is a quintessential summer fruit that's celebrated for its sweet, juicy, and refreshing qualities. Here's a detailed description of this beloved fruit

name: Carrots
description: Carrots, a versatile and nutritious vegetable that adds a burst of color and flavor to your culinary creations. Our carrots are carefully selected to ensure you experience the pure essence of freshness and crunchiness

name: Spinach
description: Spinach, a versatile and nutritious leafy green that elevates your meals with its vibrant color and health benefits. Our spinach is carefully selected to ensure you experience the essence of freshness and wholesome goodness.

name: Cabbage
description: Cabbage, a versatile and nutritious vegetable that enhances your culinary creations with its crunchy texture and health benefits. Our cabbage is carefully selected to ensure you experience the essence of freshness and wholesome goodness

name: Broccoli
description: Broccoli, a versatile and highly nutritious vegetable that adds a burst of vibrant green color, crispness, and health benefits to your meals. Our broccoli is carefully selected to ensure you experience the essence of freshness and wholesome goodness

name: Cauliflower
description: Cauliflower, a versatile and nutritious vegetable that adds a touch of crispness, mild flavor, and health benefits to your culinary creations. Our cauliflower is carefully selected to ensure you experience the essence of freshness and wholesome goodness

name: Parsley
description: Parsley, a versatile and aromatic herb that adds a burst of freshness, color, and flavor to your culinary creations. Our parsley is carefully selected to ensure you experience the essence of freshness and vibrant green goodness

name: Basil
description: Basil, an aromatic herb that infuses your culinary creations with a burst of vibrant flavor and delightful fragrance. Our basil is carefully selected to ensure you experience the essence of freshness and culinary excellence

name: Mint
description: Mint, a fragrant herb that invigorates your senses with its cooling aroma and distinctive flavor. Our mint is carefully selected to ensure you experience the essence of freshness and culinary delight

name: Rosemary
description: Rosemary, an aromatic herb that adds a touch of sophistication, a burst of fragrance, and a depth of flavor to your culinary creations. Our rosemary is carefully selected to ensure you experience the essence of freshness and culinary excellence

name: Oregano
description: Oregano, an aromatic herb that enhances your culinary creations with a burst of flavor and a touch of Mediterranean flair. Our oregano is carefully selected to ensure you experience the essence of freshness and culinary excellence

name: Saffron
description: Saffron threads, a highly prized spice known for its vibrant color, distinct flavor, and culinary excellence. Our saffron is carefully selected to ensure you experience the essence of luxury and culinary perfection

name: Tenderloin
description: Tenderloin steak, a culinary masterpiece known for its exceptional tenderness, buttery texture, and exquisite flavor. Our tenderloin is carefully selected to ensure you experience the epitome of quality and dining indulgence

name: Rib Eye
description: Ribeye steak, a culinary masterpiece renowned for its exceptional marbling, robust flavor, and succulent tenderness. Our ribeye is carefully selected to ensure you experience the pinnacle of quality and dining indulgence

name: Sirloin
description: Sirloin steak is a popular and versatile cut of beef that is known for its balanced flavor and tenderness. It is taken from the sirloin section of the cow, which is located just behind the rib section. Sirloin steaks vary in size and can be boneless or bone-in. The meat is typically lean with a moderate amount of marbling, resulting in a juicy and flavorful steak.

name: Wagyu
description: Wagyu beef is renowned for its exceptional marbling, tenderness, and rich, buttery flavor. It originates from Japanese cattle breeds known for their unique genetics and meticulous care during raising. The term "Wagyu" translates to "Japanese cow" in English.

name: Tomahawk
description: The Tomahawk steak is a dramatic and visually striking cut of beef that is essentially a ribeye steak with an elongated, frenched bone attached, resembling the handle of a tomahawk. This bone-in presentation makes it a showstopper at the dinner table.

name: T-Bone
description: The T-Bone steak is named for its T-shaped bone, which divides two cuts of beef: the strip steak (also known as the New York strip) on one side and the tenderloin (filet mignon) on the other. It offers a combination of lean and tender meat.

name: Whole Chicken
description: A whole chicken refers to an entire chicken, including the breast, thighs, wings, and drumsticks. It's typically sold with the skin intact and can be prepared in various ways, such as roasting, frying, or grilling. Whole chickens are versatile and offer different cuts for various dishes.

name: Chicken Breasts
description: Chicken breasts are boneless and skinless cuts of chicken meat known for their lean and mild flavor. They are often used in a wide range of dishes, including grilling, baking, saut√©ing, and stir-frying.

name: Chicken Thighs
description: Chicken thighs are darker meat portions known for their juiciness and slightly richer flavor compared to chicken breasts. They can be prepared boneless or bone-in and are excellent for roasting, braising, or grilling.

name: Chicken Wings
description: Chicken wings are small, flavorful portions of chicken often enjoyed as finger food or appetizers. They can be prepared in a variety of ways, including frying, baking, or grilling, and are often served with various sauces.

name: Chicken Drumsticks
description: Chicken drumsticks are dark meat cuts with a bone, often considered a favorite among children and adults alike. They are commonly seasoned and baked, fried, or grilled for a delicious and convenient meal.

name: Pork Ribs
description: Pork ribs come from the rib section of the pig and are known for their tender and flavorful meat. They are often slow-cooked, smoked, or grilled and are popular for their delicious, fall-off-the-bone texture.

name: Pork Belly
description: Pork belly is a fatty and flavorful cut that includes both meat and layers of fat. It's often used to make dishes like bacon and is also a key ingredient in various Asian cuisines, including pork belly buns and crispy pork belly.

name: Pork Loin Roast
description: Pork loin roast is a lean and tender cut of pork often seasoned and roasted. It's a versatile option for creating elegant main courses and can be sliced into pork chops.

name: Pork Shoulder
description: Pork shoulder, also known as pork butt or Boston butt, is a well-marbled cut with rich, porky flavor. It's commonly used for slow-cooked dishes like pulled pork, stews, and carnitas.

name: Pork Tenderloin
description: Pork tenderloin is a lean and tender cut of pork known for its mild flavor. It's versatile and can be prepared by roasting, grilling, or pan-searing. It's often sliced into medallions for serving.

name: Pork Chops
description: Pork chops are bone-in or boneless cuts from the loin or rib area of the pig. They are tender and juicy and can be prepared in various ways, including frying, grilling, or baking.

name: Tuna
description: Tuna is a popular fish known for its firm and meaty texture. It can be grilled, seared, or used in sushi and sashimi dishes. Tuna steaks are prized for their flavor and versatility.

name: Salmon
description: Salmon is a versatile and flavorful fish known for its rich, pink-orange flesh. It can be grilled, baked, broiled, or pan-seared and is often enjoyed for its health benefits.

name: Black cod
description: Black cod, also known as sablefish or butterfish, is a delicate and flaky fish with a mild, buttery flavor. It's often marinated and grilled or broiled to bring out its unique taste.

name: Mackerel
description: Mackerel is a fatty fish with a robust flavor. It's commonly smoked, grilled, or pan-fried and is often used in sushi and traditional dishes in various cuisines.

name: Eel
description: Eel, such as unagi and anago, is a delicacy in Japanese cuisine. It's typically grilled and glazed with a sweet and savory sauce, served over rice in sushi rolls or as part of traditional eel dishes.

name: White Egg
description: White eggs are chicken eggs with white shells. They are commonly used in baking, cooking, and as a source of protein in various dishes.

name: Brown Egg
description: Brown eggs are chicken eggs with brown shells. They have the same nutritional content as white eggs and are often preferred for their organic or free-range origins.

name: Chocolate Milk
description: Chocolate milk is a sweetened milk beverage flavored with cocoa or chocolate syrup. It's a popular choice among both children and adults for its creamy texture and chocolatey taste.

name: Strawberry Milk
description: Strawberry milk is a flavored milk drink that combines the goodness of milk with the sweet and fruity taste of strawberries. It's often enjoyed as a refreshing beverage.

name: Banana Milk
description: Banana milk is a dairy-free alternative made by blending bananas with water or a plant-based milk like almond or soy. It has a sweet and fruity flavor with a creamy texture, making it a popular choice for those seeking a non-dairy milk option.

name: Goat Milk
description: Goat milk is a milk product produced by goats. It has a distinct flavor that is often described as creamier and slightly tangier than cow's milk. Goat milk is a source of calcium, vitamins, and minerals.

name: Hazelnut Milk
description: Hazelnut milk is a dairy-free milk alternative made from ground hazelnuts and water. It has a mild nutty flavor and is often used as a lactose-free or vegan milk option.

name: Cheddar
description: Cheddar cheese is a popular and versatile cheese known for its creamy texture and sharp, tangy flavor. It can range from mild to extra sharp, with various uses in cooking and snacking.

name: Mozarella
description: Mozzarella cheese is a soft and mild cheese known for its stretchy texture when melted. It's a classic choice for pizza, caprese salad, and many Italian dishes.

name: Blue Cheese
description: Blue cheese is a type of cheese characterized by its blue or green veins of mold. It has a strong and tangy flavor with a creamy texture. It's often used in salads and dressings.

name: Ricotta
description: Ricotta cheese is a soft and creamy cheese with a slightly sweet flavor. It's commonly used in Italian cuisine, particularly in dishes like lasagna and stuffed pasta.

name: Parmesan
description: Parmesan cheese, also known as Parmigiano-Reggiano, is a hard and aged cheese with a rich, nutty flavor. It's often grated and used as a topping for pasta and salads.

name: American
description: American cheese is a processed cheese product known for its mild and creamy texture. It's a common choice for cheeseburgers, grilled cheese sandwiches, and macaroni and cheese.

name: Greek yogurt
description: Greek yogurt is a thick and creamy yogurt with a tangy flavor. It's strained to remove whey, resulting in a higher protein content compared to regular yogurt. It's often enjoyed with fruit or honey.

name: Soy yogurt
description: Soy yogurt is a dairy-free alternative to traditional yogurt made from soy milk. It has a creamy texture and can be enjoyed by those with lactose intolerance or dairy allergies.

name: Goat's milk yogurt.
description: Goat's milk yogurt is similar to traditional yogurt but made from goat's milk. It has a distinct flavor and may be easier to digest for some individuals.

name: Sheep's milk yogurt
description: Sheep's milk yogurt is made from the milk of sheep and is known for its rich and creamy texture. It has a slightly sweeter flavor compared to cow's milk yogurt.

name: Icelandic yogurt
description: Icelandic yogurt, also known as skyr, is a thick and creamy yogurt with a mild flavor. It's often high in protein and is a staple in Icelandic cuisine.

name: Normal yakult
description: Normal Yakult is a popular probiotic dairy beverage that originated in Japan. It is made from fermented milk and contains the beneficial bacteria strain known as "Lactobacillus casei Shirota.

name: Light yakult
description: Light Yakult is a variation of the traditional Yakult probiotic drink with a reduced-calorie content. It is formulated to provide the same probiotic benefits as regular Yakult but with fewer calories and less sugar.

name: Quail Egg
description: Quail eggs are small eggs laid by quail birds. They have a delicate flavor and are often used in Asian cuisine, salads, or as garnishes.

name: Duck Egg
description: Duck eggs are larger than chicken eggs and have a richer flavor and creamier yolk. They are used in various culinary applications and are favored in baking.

name: Frozen Green Beans
description: Frozen green beans are green beans that have been blanched and frozen. They are a convenient option for adding vegetables to dishes and can be steamed, boiled, or saut√©ed.

name: Frozen Broccoli
description: Frozen broccoli consists of broccoli florets that have been frozen. It's a versatile frozen vegetable that can be used in stir-fries, casseroles, and as a side dish.

name: Frozen Cauliflower
description: Frozen cauliflower includes cauliflower florets that have been frozen. It can be used as a lower-carb substitute for mashed potatoes or as a side dish.

name: Frozen Corn
description: Frozen corn is sweet corn kernels that have been frozen. It's a common addition to soups, stews, and as a side vegetable.

name: Frozen Carrots
description: Frozen carrots consist of carrot slices or chunks that have been frozen. They are used in a variety of dishes, including soups, stews, and casseroles.

name: Nugget
description: Nuggets are small, bite-sized pieces of meat or meat alternatives that are breaded and often fried. They are a popular choice among children and adults.

name: French Fries
description: French fries are thin strips of potatoes that have been fried until crispy. They are a classic side dish and snack item enjoyed with various condiments.

name: Sausage
description: Sausage is a seasoned and flavored meat product often encased in a casing. It can be made from various meats and spices and is used in a wide range of dishes.

name: Pizza
description: Pizza is a popular dish consisting of a round, flatbread crust topped with tomato sauce, cheese, and various toppings. It can be customized to suit individual preferences.

name: Dim sum
description: Dim sum is a Chinese cuisine style featuring a variety of small, flavorful dishes served in steamer baskets or on small plates. It includes items like dumplings, buns, and spring rolls.

name: Chocolate Ice Cream
description: Chocolate ice cream is a frozen dessert made with a base of milk, cream, sugar, and cocoa or chocolate. It has a rich and indulgent chocolate flavor.

name: Milo Ice Cream
description: Milo ice cream is a frozen dessert flavored with Milo, a popular chocolate and malt powder. It has a unique malty-chocolate taste and is a favorite in some regions.

name: Banana Ice Cream
description: Banana ice cream is a frozen dessert made from pureed bananas. It has a naturally sweet and creamy flavor, often without added sugar or dairy.

name: Strawberry Ice Cream
description: Strawberry ice cream is a delightful frozen dessert made with a creamy base and real or artificial strawberry flavor. It typically features pieces of strawberries or swirls of strawberry sauce for a sweet and fruity taste.

name: Vanilla Ice Cream
description: Vanilla ice cream is a classic and creamy dessert known for its rich, smooth texture and the natural flavor of vanilla beans. It serves as a versatile base for various toppings and mix-ins.

name: Wasabi Ice Cream
description: Wasabi ice cream is a unique and daring frozen treat that combines the coolness of ice cream with the intense, spicy flavor of wasabi, a Japanese horseradish. It offers a surprising and bold taste experience.

name: Baguette
description: A baguette is a long, thin French bread with a crisp crust and soft, airy interior. It's a staple of French cuisine and is often used for making sandwiches or served with cheese.

name: Croissant
description: A croissant is a buttery and flaky pastry known for its crescent shape. It's a classic French pastry enjoyed for breakfast or as a snack and can be filled with various ingredients like chocolate or almond paste.

name: white bread
description: White bread is a soft and fluffy bread made from refined wheat flour. It's a common choice for sandwiches and toast, known for its mild flavor and texture.

name: Wholegrain Bread
description: Wholegrain bread is made from whole wheat flour, retaining the bran and germ, making it a healthier option compared to white bread. It offers a nutty flavor and is rich in fiber.

name: Rye Bread
description: Rye bread is a dense and hearty bread made primarily from rye flour. It has a slightly tangy flavor and is popular in Scandinavian and Eastern European cuisines.

name: Apple pie
description: Apple pie is a classic dessert consisting of a flaky pastry crust filled with sliced apples, sugar, and spices. It's often served warm and may be topped with ice cream or whipped cream.

name: Chocolate chip cookies
description: Chocolate chip cookies are sweet, chewy cookies studded with chocolate chips or chunks. They are a beloved treat with a perfect balance of sweetness and chocolate flavor.

name: Bagels
description: Bagels are round, dense bread rings with a chewy texture. They are often boiled before baking, giving them a distinctive crust. Bagels can be sliced and toasted, then topped with various spreads.

name: Cream puffs
description: Cream puffs are delicate, hollow pastries filled with sweet whipped cream or custard. They are typically dusted with powdered sugar and make for a delightful dessert.

name: Blueberry muffins
description: Blueberry muffins are moist and tender baked treats filled with juicy blueberries. They are a popular breakfast or snack option, known for their fruity and slightly sweet flavor.

name: Red velvet cake
description: Red velvet cake is a rich and velvety dessert known for its striking red color. It's typically flavored with cocoa and buttermilk, and it's often paired with cream cheese frosting.

name: Chocolate cake
description: Chocolate cake is a decadent dessert made with cocoa or chocolate. It can vary from dark and fudgy to light and fluffy, and it's often topped with chocolate frosting.

name: Strawberry Cake
description: Strawberry cake is a sweet and fruity dessert made with strawberry-flavored cake layers and often filled with fresh strawberries or strawberry frosting.

name: Oreo cake
description: Oreo cake features layers of chocolate cake or cookies-and-cream cake with Oreo cookie pieces and a creamy filling. It's a treat for Oreo cookie enthusiasts.

name: Blueberry cake
description: Blueberry cake is a moist and flavorful dessert filled with fresh or frozen blueberries. It offers a delightful burst of berry flavor in every bite.

name: Coca-cola
description: Coca-Cola, often referred to as Coke, is a popular carbonated soft drink known for its sweet and refreshing taste. It has a distinct cola flavor and is widely enjoyed worldwide.

name: Sprite
description: Sprite is a clear and lemon-lime flavored carbonated beverage. It's known for its crisp and citrusy taste, making it a popular choice for a refreshing drink.

name: Fanta
description: Fanta is a fruity carbonated soda available in various flavors, such as orange, grape, and pineapple. It's characterized by its bold and fruity taste.

name: Mountain Dew
description: Mountain Dew is a citrus-flavored carbonated soft drink known for its vibrant green color and bold, citrusy taste. It offers a refreshing and energizing experience.

name: Pepsi
description: Pepsi is a cola-flavored carbonated soft drink similar to Coca-Cola. It has a distinctive cola taste and is a popular alternative to other cola beverages.

name: Green Tea
description: Green tea is a mild and soothing beverage made from the leaves of the Camellia sinensis plant. It's known for its earthy and slightly grassy flavor and is a source of antioxidants.

name: Jasmine Tea
description: Jasmine tea is a fragrant tea infused with jasmine blossoms. It has a delicate and floral aroma, with a subtly sweet and soothing taste.

name: Oolong Tea
description: Oolong tea is a partially oxidized tea that falls between green and black tea in terms of flavor and caffeine content. It offers a range of flavors from floral to toasty.

name: Black Tea
description: Black tea is a fully oxidized tea with a robust and bold flavor. It's commonly served with or without milk and sugar and can vary in taste from malty to fruity.

name: White Tea
description: White tea is a delicate and minimally processed tea made from young tea leaves and buds. It has a light and slightly sweet flavor with subtle floral notes.

name: Americano
description: An Americano is a coffee drink made by diluting a shot of espresso with hot water. It results in a milder coffee flavor and is often enjoyed black or with added cream and sugar.

name: Mocha
description: Mocha is a coffee beverage that combines espresso with chocolate, typically in the form of cocoa powder or chocolate syrup. It's known for its rich and indulgent flavor.

name: Cappucino
description: A cappuccino is an espresso-based coffee drink that consists of equal parts espresso, steamed milk, and milk foam. It's known for its balanced and creamy texture.

name: Latte
description: A latte is a coffee drink made with espresso and a larger amount of steamed milk. It has a mild coffee flavor and is often topped with a small amount of milk foam.

name: Espresso
description: Espresso is a concentrated coffee beverage made by forcing hot water through finely-ground coffee beans. It has a strong and bold flavor with a rich crema on top.

name: Vodka
description: Vodka is a clear and neutral spirit known for its high alcohol content and versatility in cocktails. It has a clean and neutral taste.

name: Rum
description: Rum is a distilled spirit made from sugarcane or molasses. It comes in various types, including light, dark, and spiced, with flavors ranging from sweet to robust.

name: Tequila
description: Tequila is a distilled spirit made from the fermented juice of the blue agave plant. It's known for its unique and often bold flavor, with varieties ranging from blanco (silver) to a√±ejo (aged).

name: Whiskey
description: Whiskey is a distilled spirit made from fermented grain mash, which can include barley, corn, rye, or wheat. It offers a diverse range of flavors and styles, including bourbon, Scotch, and more.

name: Gin
description: Gin is a clear spirit flavored with botanicals, primarily juniper berries. It has a distinct herbal and aromatic flavor and is a key ingredient in classic cocktails like the gin and tonic.

name: Glass and Window Cleaners
description: Glass and window cleaners are formulated to remove dirt, streaks, and smudges from glass surfaces, leaving them clear and shiny.

name: Bathroom Cleaners
description: Bathroom cleaners are specifically designed to clean and disinfect bathroom surfaces, including sinks, showers, tubs, and toilets. They help eliminate mold, mildew, and soap scum.

name: Disinfectant Cleaners
description: Disinfectant cleaners are household cleaning products that contain active ingredients designed to kill germs, bacteria, and viruses on various surfaces. They are commonly used for sanitizing.

name: Floor Cleaners
description: oor cleaners are formulated to clean and maintain different types of flooring, such as tile, hardwood, laminate, or vinyl. They help remove dirt and stains while leaving floors looking clean and shiny.

name: Laundry Detergent
description: Laundry detergent is a cleaning product specifically designed for washing clothes. It comes in various forms, including liquid, powder, and pods, and contains cleaning agents that remove dirt, stains, and odors from clothing during the washing process. Laundry detergents are available in various scents and formulations to cater to different washing machine types and laundry needs.

name: Fabric Softener
description: Fabric softener is a laundry product used in the washing machine to add a layer of softness and freshness to clothing and linens. It helps reduce static cling, makes fabrics feel smoother, and imparts a pleasant scent. Fabric softeners are available in liquid or sheet form and can enhance the comfort and aroma of freshly laundered items.

name: Bleach
description: Bleach is a powerful disinfectant and cleaning agent used to whiten and sanitize laundry, remove stains, and disinfect surfaces. It is available in both chlorine bleach and oxygen bleach varieties. Chlorine bleach is effective for whitening and disinfection, while oxygen bleach is gentler on fabrics and colored items.

name: Stain Removers
description: Stain removers are specialized cleaning products designed to target and remove specific stains, such as grease, ink, wine, or grass. They come in various forms, including sprays, gels, sticks, and pens, and are applied directly to stains before washing or as a pre-treatment to help lift and eliminate the stain.

name: Dishwasher Detergent
description: Dishwasher detergent is a cleaning product specifically formulated for use in automatic dishwashers. It contains enzymes and surfactants that break down and remove food residue and grease from dishes, glasses, and utensils. Dishwasher detergents are available in various forms, including powder, gel, and tabs, and are essential for achieving sparkling clean dishes.

name: Dishwasher Rinse Aid
description: Dishwasher rinse aid is an additive used in automatic dishwashers to improve the drying process and reduce water spots and streaks on dishes. It helps water sheet off dishes more evenly, allowing them to dry more efficiently and with a shine. Rinse aid is especially beneficial in hard water areas.

name: Dish Brush
description: A dish brush is a kitchen cleaning tool with bristles designed for scrubbing and cleaning dishes, pots, pans, and utensils. It typically has a handle for a comfortable grip and is used in conjunction with dishwashing soap to remove food residues and grease from surfaces.

name: Dishwasher Deodorizers
description: Dishwasher deodorizers are products designed to combat unpleasant odors that can develop inside dishwashers over time. They contain odor-fighting agents that help keep the dishwasher smelling fresh and clean. Deodorizers are usually placed in the dishwasher during a cycle to neutralize odors and leave a pleasant fragrance.

The bottles are made with recycled plastic and they look SO CUTE in your bathroom. We‚Äôre fans of the volume version, but they have shampoo and conditioner sets available in smoothing, repairing and, sensitive-friendly variations too.

description: Those who love affordable and natural haircare, swear by Sukin. The hydrating shampoo and conditioner combo contains shea butter and coconut to tame frizz and repair dry and damaged hair, while olive oil strengthens and adds shine.

The delicious, natural and vegan treatments are suitable for coloured hair and are a fast way to get healthy and smooth locks.

name: TRESemm√© Violet Blonde Shampoo and Conditioner

name: Olay Regenerist Micro-Sculpting Cream
description: Olay Regenerist Micro-Sculpting Cream is a high-performance anti-aging moisturizer. It is designed to hydrate and revitalize the skin, reducing the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles. This cream is known for its advanced formula that contains ingredients to promote firmer, more youthful-looking skin.

name: Cetaphil Daily Hydrating Lotion with Hyaluronic Acid
description: Cetaphil Daily Hydrating Lotion is a lightweight, non-greasy moisturizer enriched with hyaluronic acid. It is specially formulated to provide long-lasting hydration to the skin while maintaining a gentle and non-irritating formula suitable for daily use.

name: Olay Advanced Cleansing System
description: The Olay Advanced Cleansing System is an electronic facial cleansing brush designed to exfoliate and cleanse the skin effectively. It helps remove dirt, oil, and makeup, leaving the skin feeling smoother and refreshed.

name: Garnier Skin Active Hydra Bomb Tissue Face Mask Green Tea
description: The Garnier Skin Active Hydra Bomb Tissue Face Mask infused with green tea extract is a sheet mask designed to hydrate and refresh the skin. It provides a relaxing and nourishing experience, leaving the skin feeling revitalized and glowing.

name: Asda Protect Moisturising Sun Lotion SPF30
description: Asda Protect Moisturising Sun Lotion SPF30 is a sunscreen lotion designed to protect the skin from harmful UV rays while providing moisturization. It's suitable for use during outdoor activities and offers broad-spectrum sun protection.

name: Asda Protect Refreshing Clear Sun Spray SPF30
description: Asda Protect Refreshing Clear Sun Spray SPF30 is a convenient sunscreen spray that offers easy application and effective sun protection. It helps prevent sunburn and can be used on both the body and face.

name: Boots Soltan Protect & Moisturise Lotion
description: Boots Soltan Protect & Moisturise Lotion is a sun protection lotion that combines SPF with moisturizing properties. It helps keep the skin hydrated while guarding against sun damage.

name: Boots Soltan Kids Protect & Moisturise Lotion
description: Boots Soltan Kids Protect & Moisturise Lotion is a sunblock lotion specially formulated for children's sensitive skin. It provides SPF protection while helping to keep their skin soft and moisturized.

name: SEVEN SEAS HIGADO 170ML
